This repository is the open-source foundation of AlphaSub, a native macOS
subtitling application. It contains the subtitle data model and the freely
available subtitle format handlers. The AlphaSub application (its UI, on-device
AI, professional broadcast/cinema delivery formats, and licensing) is not part
of this repository.
